<bibRefCitation box="[1088,1219,757,782]" pageId="1" pageNumber="396" refId="ref5533" refString="Hyatt, K. H. (1954) The African spiders of the family Ctenidae in the collections of the British Museum (Natural History). Annals and Magazine of Natural History, 7, 877 - 894. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222935408651809" type="journal article">Hyatt 1954</bibRefCitation>
